  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110099401074\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110099401074\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\">체형교정의 치료 효과</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\">&nbsp; <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">척추와 골격이 이상적인 정렬을 이룰 때 우리몸의 디스크와 관절은 정상기능을 수행할 수 있습니다. 그러나 굽어지거나, 일자가 되거나 틀어지거나 하게 되면 디스크가 눌리거나, 관절이 한쪽만 닳게 되거나 움직일 때마다 소리가 나거나 하는 등 기능 및 구조상의 문제가 발생하게 되고, 통증으로 이어집니다.</span></strong> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_37/isuhani_1292903782129L6rTk_JPEG/4_image_05.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"511\" height=\"483\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20101221_37/isuhani_1292903782129L6rTk_JPEG/4_image_05.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26F8972')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_37/isuhani_1292903782129L6rTk_JPEG/4_image_05.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><?xml:namespace prefix = v ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" /><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" stroked=\"f\" filled=\"f\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" o:spt=\"75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"></v:stroke><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 