 align=\"left\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); CLEAR: left; BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)\" id=\"20101221_97/isuhani_1292904006238kneFX_JPEG/%BE%E7%B4%DE%B8%B7_%B1%B3%C1%A4%C0%FC-1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26F8972')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_97/isuhani_1292904006238kneFX_JPEG/%BE%E7%B4%DE%B8%B7_%B1%B3%C1%A4%C0%FC-1.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_194/isuhani_1292904006502bO3f1_JPEG/%BE%E7%B4%DE%B8%B7_%B1%B3%C1%A4%C8%C4-1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"255\" height=\"187\" align=\"right\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); CLEAR: right; BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0)\" id=\"20101221_194/isuhani_1292904006502bO3f1_JPEG/%BE%E7%B4%DE%B8%B7_%B1%B3%C1%A4%C8%C4-1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26F8972')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_194/isuhani_1292904006502bO3f1_JPEG/%BE%E7%B4%DE%B8%B7_%B1%B3%C1%A4%C8%C4-1.jpg?type=w3\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p></span></strong><strong><o:p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</o:p>&nbsp;</strong> \r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><o:p></o:p></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">그러나 하지길이 차이나 척추 골반이 복합적으로 틀어진 경우, 턱관절이 같이 틀어진 경우 등은 10여회~ 길게는 30회정도 교정을 해야하는 경우도 있습니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림체; mso-ascii-font-family: 굴림체; mso-hansi-font-family: 굴림체\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">목, 허리 디스크. 어깨, 무릎 관절통. 만성적인 목, 어깨, 허리 통증. 팔 다리 저림. 만성피로. 집중력 저하. 만성두통. 여성의 자궁질환(생리통 등). 등이 체형치료의 대상이 됩니다. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span><o:p></o:p></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"바탕글\"><strong><o:p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_85/isuhani_1292904133433Kf5G8_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20101221_85/isuhani_1292904133433Kf5G8_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26F8972')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101221_85/isuhani_1292904133433Kf5G8_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></o:p></strong></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
